Fast Movement			KEY:Barbarian ~ Fast Movement				SORTKEY:Class_Barbarian	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.BarbarianClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																													DESC:A barbarian's land speed is faster than the norm for his race by +10 feet. This benefit applies only when he is wearing no armor, light armor, or medium armor and not carrying a heavy load. Apply this bonus before modifying the barbarian's speed because of any load carried or armor worn.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				BONUS:MOVEADD|TYPE=Walk|10|TYPE=FastMove|PREVARLT:ENCUMBERANCE,2,var("COUNT[EQTYPE.ARMOR.IS.HEAVY]"),1																																																					SOURCELONG:Revised (v.3.5) System Reference Document	SOURCESHORT:RSRD		SOURCEPAGE:classesI

Weapon and Armor Proficiency	KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency		SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:A Valroux Swordsman is proficient with all non-exotic fencing blades and non-exotic small blades. The school does not encourage the use of armor or shields by its students.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																AUTO:WEAPONPROF|TYPE=Fencing|TYPE=SmallBlade																																																																	SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
Focused Training			KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Focused Training				SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 1st level, students of this school receive the feats: Weapon Specialization (Rapier) and Weapon Specialization (Main Gauche).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Weapon Specialization (Rapier)|Weapon Specialization (Main Gauche)																																SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
Off-Hand Fighting			KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Off-Hand Fighting			SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 1st level, when wearing light or no armor and armed with a small blade in their off-hand, astudent of this school can fight with two weapons as if he had the feats: Two-Weapon Fighting and Improved Two-Weapon Fighting.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Two-Weapon Fighting|Improved Two-Weapon Fighting|PREMULT:2,[!PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Armor.Medium,TYPE=Armor.Heavy],[PREEQUIPSECONDARY:1,TYPE=SmallBlade]																																																		SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
Bonus Feats				KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Bonus Feats				SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 2nd level, a student of this school gets a bonus feat as a fighter of the same level. He gains an additional bonus feat at 4th level.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											ADD:ABILITY|1|FEAT|NORMAL|TYPE=Fighter																																					SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
Raise the Stakes			KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Raise the Stakes				SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 3rd level, Valroux students have learned how to "raise the stakes" in a fight. When wielding a fencing blade in their primary hand and a small blade in their offhand the student may fight as if he had the feats: Combat Expertise and Power Attack.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																								ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Combat Expertise|Power Attack|PREMULT:2,[PREEQUIPPRIMARY:1,TYPE=Fencing],[PREEQUIPSECONDARY:1,TYPE=SmallBlade]																																																		SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
Nimble				KEY:Valroux Swordsman ~ Nimble					SORTKEY:Class_ValrouxSwordsman	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.ClassFeatures.ValrouxSwordsmanClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:At 5th level, Valroux rank among the fastest swordsmen in the world. Students of this school gain a +1 competence bonus to their Dex rolls and affiliated checks (even attack rolls when applicable ). This does not apply to a character's Ref saves. Additionally the student gains a +4 competence bonus to his Tumble skill checks.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											BONUS:STAT|DEX|2|TYPE=Competence	BONUS:SKILL|Tumble|4|TYPE=Competence		BONUS:SAVE|BASE.Reflex|-1									SOURCEPAGE:pg. 98
